001	Welcome to THE ALCHEMIST CODE. My name is Ouroboros and I am here to get you ready for your journey.
002	Looks like you have completed a mission! Let's check it out!
002b	Tap on Missions now!
003	On the Daily tab, you can view missions that you complete daily. Let's check out Milestones.
003b	Milestones are grouped into categories that can be accessed by tapping on their respective tab. Tap on the highlighted tab.
004	Tap on the Completed! button to collect your reward.
005	Details of your rewards will appear here. Tap OK.
006	Let's head back to the capital now.
007	We will need more strength for the journey ahead. Let's summon more allies now.
008	Here you can see the available summons. Tap the button to proceed.
009	You can see unit details here. Tap OK to proceed.
009b	It appears you obtained Soul Shards! They can be even more useful than new characters. Tap OK to proceed.
010	Tap on the Home Icon to return.
011	You have completed a Challenge. Tap on Claim to see more details.
012	Tap on the Challenge to claim your reward.
013	Rewards will be sent to Gifts on the Home Screen.
014	Let's head back to the capital now.
015	Let's take a look at units in detail. Tap on Menu.
016	Now, tap on Units.
017	Here you can see all your available units. Let's look at Logi in detail.
018	You can view unit stats, evolution stages and equipped items here.
019	Let's make Logi stronger. Tap on the equipment slot.
020	Here you can see a piece of equipment's details. Tap Equip to let Logi use it.
021	When all six pieces are equipped, you can do a JobLv Up to increase Logi's stats and gain new Abilities.
022	Tap on Abilities to view Logi's available abilities.
023	You can tap and hold each Ability to see more info. Let's Level Up an Ability right now.
024	New Skills like this one will appear once you unlock them. Tap anywhere on the popup to continue.
025	Another way to strengthen Logi is to Limit Break. Let's do that now.
026	Limit Breaking a unit increases its max level limit and also unlocks new job classes. Tap limit break now.
026b	Always be on the lookout for more Soul Shards to unleash their full potential!
027	Tap on Evolve now.
028	This window shows the requirements for evolution. By evolving a unit, its max level and max job level increase. Close this window.
029	Next, let's look at Ability Setup.
030	As you unlock more jobs and abilities, you can set them up here. That’s all for units for now!
031	Let's head Home.
032	Let's start our Quest.
033	Tap on Story to continue.
034	To see more details about a quest, tap the magnifying glass icon to its right. But for now, select the quest by tapping on it.
035	On this Quest Prep screen, you can choose which Units and Items to bring into battle.
036	You can also hire a Mercenary to join you in battle.
037	Tap on Go! to start our Quest.
038	You are now set to venture forth on your own! I hope you enjoy playing THE ALCHEMIST CODE.
